data.description: BEAUTIFUL and WELL-MAINTAINED 3 bedroom brick Natrona Heights home. Situated on a large level lot in on a friendly street, this recently-renovated home features a galley-style kitchen with stainless steel appliances, maple cabinets, silver fleck quartz countertops, recessed lighting and ceramic tile flooring, and a center island that opens to the beautiful over-sized dining room. The spacious living room includes a decorative gas fireplace and recessed lighting. Three bedrooms upstairs, and the master suite has a massive 10x8 walk-in closet and an amazing 13X10 en suite bath with a 6 ft. long soaker tub and a over-sized tiled / stone shower with built-in Bluetooth. New furnace / A/C, newer roof, updated plumbing & electric. Hardwired CO2 & smoke detectors, custom blinds, flooring & lighting throughout.
